article.headline: Southern deals Mississippi Valley State 23rd straight loss 78-54
article.description: — Tai'Reon Joseph had 18 points, Brandon Davis scored 16 and Southern beat Mississippi Valley State 78-54 on Monday night, handing the Delta Devils their 23rd straight loss dating to last season.
article.linkText: Southern deals Mississippi Valley State 23rd straight loss 78-54
article.story: BATON ROUGE, La. -- — Tai'Reon Joseph had 18 points, Brandon Davis scored 16 and Southern beat Mississippi Valley State 78-54 on Monday night, handing the Delta Devils their 23rd straight loss dating to last season. Joseph and Davis both made 4 of 8 shots from 3-point range for the Jaguars (11-9, 5-2 Southwestern Athletic Conference). Derrick Tezeno scored 10. Arecko Gipson had 17 points and Rayquan Brown scored 16 with both grabbing six rebounds for the Delta Devils (0-21, 0-8). ------ Get poll alerts and updates on AP Top 25 basketball throughout the season.
